#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:2
msgid "状态看板与指令"
msgstr "Status Dashboard and Instructions"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:8
msgid "状态看板"
msgstr "Status Dashboard"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:9
msgid ""
"状态看板实际上是一个默认随着插件开机自启动的controller，名称为fairino_hardware_state_broadcaster，它以500HZ的频率监控插件中所有状态反馈接口，并以topic的形式发布出来，消息类型名称是fairino_hardware_state_broadcaster/msg/HardwareState。"
msgstr ""
"The status dashboard is essentially a controller named "
"“fairino_hardware_state_broadcaster” that starts automatically with the "
"plugin by default. It monitors all status feedback interfaces within the "
"plugin at a frequency of 500 Hz and publishes the data as topics, with the "
"message type name being "
"“fairino_hardware_state_broadcaster/msg/HardwareState”."

