#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:114
msgid ""
"其中，hexerrorcode_curerrcode是当前系统的错误码，一旦该数值为非0，说明系统存在错误，由于错误码显示使用了十进制，而编写错误码采用了十六进制，因此需要讲十进制数据转换成十六进制数，才能解析出错误码对应的故障信息，以下是32位错误码组成说明。"
msgstr ""
"Here, “hexerrorcode_curerrcode” is the current system error code. If this "
"value is non-zero, it indicates that an error exists in the system. Since "
"the displayed error code uses decimal notation while the error codes are "
"defined in hexadecimal, the decimal value must be converted to hexadecimal "
"to interpret the corresponding fault information. Below is an explanation of"
" the 32-bit error code structure."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:117
msgid "表2-2 插件32位错误码组成说明表"
msgstr "Table 2-2: Description of 32-bit Plugin Error Codes"

