#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:151
msgid ""
"请注意，目前规定致命级别的错误不支持错误恢复，错误级别的均可以通过指令服务器的reseterror指令恢复，警告级别的信息会通过curwarncode提示但是不会中断系统运行。"
msgstr ""
"Note that fatal-level errors currently do not support error recovery; all "
"error-level issues can be recovered via the server’s “reseterror” command; "
"warning-level messages are indicated by “curwarncode” but do not interrupt "
"system operation."

