#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:194
msgid "HAL 库掉线或底层驱动进程死掉。排查底层 igh 进程是否正常存活，检查 IPC 共享内存机制是否被阻塞。"
msgstr ""
"The HAL library has gone offline or the underlying driver process has "
"crashed. Check whether the underlying igh process is running normally and "
"verify whether the IPC shared memory mechanism is blocked."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:196
msgid "0x0F100101"
msgstr "0x0F100101"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:197
msgid "从站信息和校验错误"
msgstr "Slave Information and Checksum Errors"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:198
msgid "底层获取的伺服数据包 CRC 校验失败。重点检查总线网线是否松动、水晶头是否良好，或线缆是否受到强电磁干扰。"
msgstr ""
"CRC verification failure for the servo data packet obtained at the lower "
"layer. Pay special attention to whether the bus network cable is loose, "
"whether the RJ-45 connector is intact, or whether the cable is subject to "
"strong electromagnetic interference."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:200
msgid "0x0F100102"
msgstr "0x0F100102"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:201
msgid "从站数量或类型异常"
msgstr "Abnormal number or type of slave stations"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:202
