msgstr ""
"The actual number/model of physically scanned joints is inconsistent with "
"the topology defined in the YAML configuration file. Check whether the "
"configuration file is loaded correctly."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:204
msgid "0x0F100103"
msgstr "0x0F100103"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:205
msgid "状态共享内存指针为空"
msgstr "Status shared memory pointer is null"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:206
msgid "内存映射失败。ROS 2 hardware_interface 无法正确挂载读取机械臂状态的共享内存地址。"
msgstr ""
"Memory mapping failed. The ROS 2 hardware_interface failed to correctly "
"mount the shared memory address for reading the robotic arm’s status."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:208
msgid "0x0F100201"
msgstr "0x0F100201"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:209
msgid "指令共享内存指针为空"
msgstr "Instruction shared memory pointer is null"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:210
msgid "内存映射失败。ROS 2 hardware_interface 无法正确挂载下发运动指令的共享内存地址。"
msgstr ""
"Memory mapping failed. The ROS 2 hardware_interface cannot correctly mount "
"the shared memory address for issuing motion commands."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:213
msgid ""
"请注意，在系统刚启动的时候，解析出来的错误码可能在以上表格中找不到，比如会出现0x0F00005，这个错误码是0x0F00001和0x0F00004的组合，因为在系统初始化的时候，进行一系列的操作均可能出现错误，但是系统没启动之前，这些错误无法立即给出，只能采用叠加累计的方式，因此会在初始化后出现这种组合错误码。"
msgstr ""
"Note that immediately after system startup, the parsed error codes may not "
"be found in the table above—for example, 0x0F00005 may appear. This error "
"code is a combination of 0x0F00001 and 0x0F00004, because multiple "
"operations during system initialization may each fail; however, before the "
"system fully starts up, these errors cannot be reported immediately and are "
"instead accumulated cumulatively, resulting in such composite error codes "
"appearing after initialization."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:216
msgid "表2-4 错误(ERROR)级别错误码"
msgstr "Table 2-4 ERROR-Level Error Codes"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:226
msgid "0x0E10FF01"
msgstr "0x0E10FF01"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:227
msgid "驱动器故障 (全局广播)"
msgstr "Drive Failure (Global Broadcast)"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:228
msgid "0xFF 代表任意轴的广播报警。电机可能发生了过流、过载、碰撞导致过力矩，或编码器掉线。需结合单轴 errorcode 进一步定位具体关节。"
msgstr ""
"0xFF indicates a broadcast alarm for any axis. Possible causes include "
"overcurrent, overload, excessive torque due to collision, or encoder "
"disconnection. Refer to the individual-axis error code to pinpoint the "
"specific joint."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:230
msgid "0x0E100001"
msgstr "0x0E100001"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:231
msgid "软急停触发"
msgstr "Soft Emergency Stop Triggered"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:232
msgid "逻辑急停被拍下。上位机或示教器下发了紧急停止指令，底层立刻中断当前运动队列以保障安全。"
msgstr ""
"Logical emergency stop triggered. The host computer or teach pendant issued "
"an emergency stop command, causing the underlying system to immediately "
"interrupt the current motion queue to ensure safety."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:234
msgid "0x0E100002"
msgstr "0x0E100002"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:235
msgid "指令队列长度过长"
msgstr "Instruction queue is too long"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:236
msgid "插补缓冲区溢出。上位机下发轨迹点位过密或控制频率过高，导致底层消费者处理超时。需检查控制器执行频率设置。"
msgstr ""
"Interpolation buffer overflow. The host computer sends trajectory points too"
" densely or sets the control frequency too high, causing timeout in the "
"underlying consumer processing. Please check the controller’s execution "
"frequency setting."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:239
msgid "表2-5 警告(WARN)级别错误码"
msgstr "Table 2-5 Warning (WARN)-Level Error Codes"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:246
msgid "**警告释义**"
msgstr "**Warning Interpretation**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:249
msgid "0x02100001"
msgstr "0x02100001"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:250
msgid "指令步进较大 (触发削峰)"
msgstr "Large instruction step (triggering clipping)"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:251
msgid "规划器下发的相邻两点位置差值超过了底层的最大速度/加速度限制，底层强制进行了削峰平滑。可能会导致实际轨迹与预期有极小偏差。"
msgstr ""
"The positional difference between two consecutive points issued by the "
"planner exceeds the underlying system’s maximum velocity/acceleration "
"limits, triggering forced peak clipping and smoothing. This may cause a "
"negligible deviation between the actual and intended trajectory."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:253
msgid "0x02100002"
msgstr "0x02100002"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:254
msgid "指令队列写入失败"
msgstr "Instruction queue write failure"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:255
msgid "瞬时并发过高，导致系统在极短瞬间无法将插补点推入无锁队列，可能引起短暂的运动卡顿。"
msgstr ""
"Excessively high instantaneous concurrency causes the system to fail to push"
" interpolation points into the lock-free queue within an extremely short "
"time, potentially resulting in brief motion stuttering."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:258
msgid "指令服务器"
msgstr "Command Server"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:259
msgid ""
"指令服务器是随着插件系统默认开机自启动的一个controller，名称是fairino_hardware_command_controller，它对外提供了一个名称为command的action服务器，其自定义交互消息格式为："
msgstr ""
"The instruction server is a controller that starts automatically with the "
"plugin system upon boot-up, named “fairino_hardware_command_controller.” It "
"provides an action server externally named “command,” using a custom "
"interaction message format:"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:262
msgid "表2-6 自定义交互消息格式"
msgstr "Table 2-6 Custom Interactive Message Format"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:268
msgid "string command"
msgstr "string command"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:269
msgid "Request (Goal) - 字符串指令，例如 \"Enable(1)\""
msgstr "Request (Goal) – String command, e.g., \"Enable(1)\""

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:271
msgid "string error_code"
msgstr "string error_code"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:272
msgid "Result - 控制器专属 16位 Hex 错误码，例如 \"0xC000\""
msgstr ""
"Result – Controller-specific 16-bit hexadecimal error code, e.g., \"0xC000\""

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:274
msgid "float32 progress"
msgstr "float32 progress"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:275
msgid "Feedback - 执行进度 (0.0 ~ 100.0)"
msgstr "Feedback – Execution Progress (0.0 ~ 100.0)"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:278
msgid "表2-7 目前支持的指令表"
msgstr "Table 2-7 Supported Instructions"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:284
msgid "**指令名称**"
msgstr "**Instruction Name**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:285
msgid "**功能深度描述**"
msgstr "**In-depth Feature Description**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:286
msgid "**输入参数说明**"
msgstr "**Input Parameter Description**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:288
msgid "activatecontroller"
msgstr "activateController"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:289
msgid ""
"激活指定的 ROS 2 控制器。通过调用 controller_manager 的服务，将目标控制器状态从 inactive 切换为 active。"
msgstr ""
"Activate the specified ROS 2 controller by calling the controller_manager "
"service to transition the target controller’s state from inactive to active."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:290
#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:294
msgid "args[0]: 控制器名称 (String)示例: fairino_trajectory_controller"
msgstr ""
"args[0]: Controller name (String) Example: fairino_trajectory_controller"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:292
msgid "deactivatecontroller"
msgstr "Deactivate controller"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:293
msgid "停用指定的 ROS 2 控制器。将正在运行的控制器状态切换为 inactive，常用于控制权交接（如切出轨迹控制，切入阻抗控制）。"
msgstr ""
"Deactivate the specified ROS 2 controller. Switch the running controller’s "
"state to inactive, commonly used for control authority handover (e.g., "
"switching out trajectory control and switching in impedance control)."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:296
msgid "enable"
msgstr "enable"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:297
msgid "机器人使能 (Servo ON)。向下位机发送指令，闭合继电器，给各关节伺服电机上电并开启力矩输出。"
msgstr ""
"Robot Enable (Servo ON). Send a command to the lower-level controller to "
"close the relay, power up the joint servo motors, and enable torque output."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:298
msgid "无参数的情况下是全部关节使能，有参数的情况按照Bit位使能(比如1是第一关节，2是第二关节，4是第三关节，8是第四关节，7是一二三关节)"
msgstr ""
"When no parameters are provided, all joints are enabled; when parameters are"
" provided, joints are enabled according to bit positions (e.g., 1 enables "
"joint 1, 2 enables joint 2, 4 enables joint 3, 8 enables joint 4, and 7 "
"enables joints 1, 2, and 3)."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:300
msgid "disable"
msgstr "disable"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:301
msgid "机器人下使能 (Servo OFF)。切断伺服电机力矩输出，机械臂进入抱闸（Brake）状态。"
msgstr ""
"Robot servo disable (Servo OFF). Cuts off torque output from the servo "
"motors, causing the robotic arm to engage the brake."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:302
msgid "同enable函数用法"
msgstr "Same usage as the enable function"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:304
msgid "setdo"
msgstr "setdo"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:305
msgid "设置数字输出 (Digital Output)。控制机器人控制柜或末端工具的 IO 针脚电平，用于触发外围设备（如夹爪、焊枪、继电器）。"
msgstr ""
"Configure digital output to control the IO pin levels of the robot control "
"cabinet or end-effector, enabling activation of peripheral devices (e.g., "
"grippers, welding torches, relays)."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:306
msgid "args[0]: IO 端口索引/名称args[1]: 状态 (\"1\"/\"true\" 开, \"0\"/\"false\" 关)"
msgstr ""
"args[0]: IO port index/name  \n"
"args[1]: Status (\"1\"/\"true\" for on, \"0\"/\"false\" for off)"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:308
msgid "zeroing"
msgstr "zeroing"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:309
msgid "执行机械臂零点标定。触发底层寻零逻辑，使关节自动寻找机械原点并重置绝对编码器偏置。"
msgstr ""
"Perform zero-point calibration of the robotic arm. Trigger the underlying "
"homing logic to enable joints to automatically locate the mechanical origin "
"and reset the absolute encoder offset."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:310
msgid "同enable用法"
msgstr "Same usage as enable"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:312
msgid "reseterror"
msgstr "reset error"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:313
msgid "错误复位。当底层触发 ERROR 报警导致抱闸后，如果物理故障已解除，调用此指令清除底层错误标志，使系统恢复待机状态。"
msgstr ""
"Error reset. When the underlying system triggers an ERROR alarm causing "
"brake engagement, invoking this command clears the underlying error flag and"
" restores the system to standby mode, provided the physical fault has been "
"resolved."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:314
msgid "无参数"
msgstr "No parameters"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:316
msgid "frconfig"
msgstr "frconfig"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:317
msgid ""
"动态生成机器人的核心配置文件。拉起后台 Python 脚本，解析 YAML 配置，动态生成 URDF 模型和 controller_manager "
"配置文件。"
msgstr ""
"Dynamically generate the robot’s core configuration files. Launch the "
"background Python script to parse the YAML configuration and dynamically "
"generate the URDF model and controller_manager configuration files."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:318
msgid ""
"args[0] (可选): /opt/fairino_art_plugin/config文件夹下配置文件名。若为空，默认使用 "
"\"fairino_config.yaml\"，等同于frconfig(fairino_config.yaml)"
msgstr ""
"args[0] (optional): The configuration file name under the "
"`/opt/fairino_art_plugin/config` directory. If omitted, the default file "
"`\"fairino_config.yaml\"` is used, equivalent to "
"`frconfig(fairino_config.yaml)`."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:320
msgid "upgradeplugin"
msgstr "upgrade plugin"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:321
msgid "自动升级底层驱动与插件包。解压传入的 zip 包，清理旧环境，将新代码覆盖至 /opt 系统目录，并自动修复 .sh 及可执行文件的权限。"
msgstr ""
"Automatically upgrade underlying drivers and plugin packages. Extract the "
"incoming ZIP package, clean up the old environment, overwrite the new code "
"to the /opt system directory, and automatically fix permissions for .sh and "
"executable files."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:322
msgid "args[0]: 升级包 .zip 的绝对路径。示例: [\"/tmp/update_v2.zip\"]"
msgstr ""
"args[0]: The absolute path of the upgrade package (.zip). Example: "
"[\"/tmp/update_v2.zip\"]"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:324
msgid "packlog"
msgstr "PackLog"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:325
msgid ""
"一键打包系统日志与 Dump 故障快照。将 /home/fairino/plugin_log/ "
"下的故障快照及系统运行日志压缩成一个归档文件，方便现场人员拷贝导出。"
msgstr ""
"One-click packaging of system logs and dump snapshots. Compresses fault "
"snapshots and system runtime logs from /home/fairino/plugin_log/ into a "
"single archive file for easy copying and export by on-site personnel."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:326
msgid "无参数 (或可选传入目标导出路径)"
msgstr "No parameters (or optionally specify the target export path)"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:328
msgid "recorddata"
msgstr "record data"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:329
msgid "控制用户高频数据录制器。在内存中开启/关闭 20MB 的循环数据录制队列，用于抓取高精度的关节位置、力矩及状态波形。"
msgstr ""
"Control the user’s high-frequency data recorder. Enable or disable a 20 MB "
"circular data recording queue in memory for capturing high-precision joint "
"position, torque, and status waveforms."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:330
msgid "args[0]: 动作指令。仅接受 \"start\" 或 \"stop\" (忽略大小写)。"
msgstr ""
"args[0]: Action command. Only \"start\" or \"stop\" is accepted (case-"
"insensitive)."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:332
msgid ""
"同样的，根据上面阐述的指令服务器交互信息格式，每个一string指令都会有一个string反馈值，这个返回值是16位的错误码系统，其具体函数见如下表格："
msgstr ""
"Similarly, according to the instruction-server interaction format described "
"above, each string instruction has a corresponding string feedback value—a "
"16-bit error code system, whose specific functions are detailed in the table"
" below:"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:335
msgid "表2-8 具体函数表"
msgstr "Table 2-8 Specific Function Table"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:341
msgid "**返回值**"
msgstr "**Return Value**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:342
msgid "**触发场景释义**"
msgstr "**Trigger Scenario Definition**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:343
msgid "**常见排查与处理建议**"
msgstr "**Common Troubleshooting and Resolution Recommendations**"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:345
msgid "\"0xC000\""
msgstr "0xC000"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:346
msgid "执行成功。指令完整拉起并顺利结束。"
msgstr ""
"Execution succeeded. The command was fully launched and completed "
"successfully."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:347
msgid "无需处理，上位机可继续下发后续流程。"
msgstr ""
"No action required; the host computer can continue issuing subsequent "
"procedures."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:349
msgid "\"0xC010\""
msgstr "0xC010"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:350
msgid "参数非法或防注入拦截。传入参数为空，或包含危险 Shell 字符。"
msgstr ""
"Invalid parameter or injection prevention intercepted. The input parameter "
"is empty or contains dangerous shell characters."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:351
msgid "检查上位机下发的参数，确保仅包含合法文件路径或纯文本。"
msgstr ""
"Check the parameters sent by the host computer to ensure they contain only "
"valid file paths or plain text."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:353
msgid "\"0xC011\""
msgstr "0xC011"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:354
msgid "依赖服务不可用。试图调用的 ROS 2 内部服务（如 controller_manager）掉线或未就绪。"
msgstr ""
"Dependent service is unavailable. The ROS 2 internal service being called "
"(e.g., controller_manager) is offline or not ready."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:355
msgid "检查目标节点是否存活，或等待系统完全启动后再下发指令。"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the target node is alive, or wait until the system has fully "
"booted before issuing commands."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:357
msgid "\"0xC012\""
msgstr "0xC012"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:358
msgid "硬件状态异常。在下发需要硬件配合的指令时，检测到底层处于报错或未使能状态。"
msgstr ""
"Hardware status is abnormal. An error or disabled state was detected at the "
"underlying level when issuing commands requiring hardware cooperation."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:359
msgid "请先查阅 fairino_hardware 的硬件报警码，复位硬件后再试。"
msgstr ""
"Please first check the hardware alarm codes for fairino_hardware, then reset"
" the hardware and try again."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:361
msgid "\"0xC013\""
msgstr "0xC013"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:362
msgid "指令超时。指令在规定时间内未完成（如下载、系统响应等）。"
msgstr ""
"Command timeout. The command did not complete within the specified time "
"(e.g., download, system response, etc.)."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:363
msgid "检查网络连接或系统负载是否过高。"
msgstr "Check the network connection or whether the system load is too high."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:365
msgid "\"0xC020\""
msgstr "0xC020"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:366
msgid "控制器切换失败。软切换（如从关节空间切换到笛卡尔空间 Controller）被系统拒绝。"
msgstr ""
"Controller switching failed. The soft switch (e.g., from joint space to "
"Cartesian space controller) was rejected by the system."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:367
msgid "检查控制器名称是否拼写正确，或控制器端口占用冲突"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the controller name is spelled correctly, or whether there is "
"a port conflict on the controller."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:369
msgid "\"0xC021\""
msgstr "0xC021"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:370
msgid "校零超时。"
msgstr "Zero calibration timeout."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:371
msgid "检查插件是否正常运行中"
msgstr "Checking if the plugin is running normally"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:373
msgid "\"0xC030\""
msgstr "\"0xC030\""

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:374
msgid "配置生成失败。Python 脚本解析 YAML 或生成 URDF/控制器配置失败。"
msgstr ""
"Configuration generation failed. The Python script failed to parse the YAML "
"or generate the URDF/controller configuration."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:375
msgid "检查 YAML 格式是否正确，文件是否人为篡改或者出现乱码"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the YAML format is correct, and whether the file has been "
"manually tampered with or contains garbled characters."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:377
msgid "\"0xC040\""
msgstr "0xC040"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:378
msgid "解压升级包失败。unzip 指令返回非零退出码。"
msgstr ""
"Failed to extract the upgrade package. The unzip command returned a non-zero"
" exit code."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:379
msgid "检查 .zip 文件路径是否正确、压缩包是否损坏或 /tmp 空间是否满。"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the .zip file path is correct, whether the archive is "
"corrupted, or whether the /tmp space is full."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:381
msgid "\"0xC041\""
msgstr "0xC041"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:382
msgid "目录覆盖失败。插件升级覆盖到 /opt/... 目录时出错。"
msgstr ""
"Directory overwrite failed. An error occurred while the plugin upgrade "
"attempted to overwrite the /opt/... directory."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:383
msgid "检查目录的权限归属（属主是否为 fairino）或是否被占用。"
msgstr ""
"Check the directory permissions and ownership (whether the owner is fairino)"
" or whether it is occupied."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:385
msgid "\"0xC050\""
msgstr "0xC050"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:386
msgid "打包日志失败。收集、压缩 Dump 文件及系统运行日志时报错。"
msgstr ""
"Failed to package logs. An error occurred while collecting and compressing "
"dump files and system runtime logs."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:387
msgid "检查目标存储路径权限及磁盘剩余容量。"
msgstr ""
"Check the permissions of the target storage path and the remaining disk "
"capacity."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:389
msgid "\"0xC060\""
msgstr "\"0xC060\""

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:390
msgid "数据记录操作失败。recorddata(start/stop) 指令处理失败或写入异常。"
msgstr ""
"Data recording operation failed. The recorddata(start/stop) command "
"processing failed or a write exception occurred."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:391
msgid "检查 /tmp/record_data 目录是否可写，或内存中是否存在死锁。"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the /tmp/record_data directory is writable, or whether a "
"deadlock exists in memory."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:393
msgid "\"0xC0FE\""
msgstr "0xC0FE"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:394
msgid "未知指令。上位机发送了一个 Action Server 无法解析的命令字。"
msgstr ""
"Unknown command. The host computer sent a command that the Action Server "
"cannot parse."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:395
msgid "对齐上位机与下位机的通信协议接口文档。"
msgstr ""
"Alignment of the communication protocol interface documentation between the "
"host computer and the slave computer."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:397
msgid "\"0xC0FF\""
msgstr "0xC0FF"

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:398
msgid "底层抛出异常。C++ 或脚本内部发生未捕获的严重崩溃/被系统强杀。"
msgstr ""
"An exception was thrown at the lower level. A severe crash occurred inside "
"C++ or a script, or the process was forcibly terminated by the system."

#: ../../source/PluginManual/plugin_board.rst:399
msgid "需查看宿主机 dmesg 或节点标准输出，排查段错误（Segfault）或依赖丢失。"
msgstr ""
"Check the host’s dmesg or the node’s standard output to troubleshoot "
"segmentation faults (segfaults) or missing dependencies."
